snippet.title: Neo XYX Full Game Play 1080P 60FPS Sega Dreamcast
snippet.description: Since I can now capture Dreamcast games in VGA and get the correct aspect ratio I decided to take on Neo XYX again and after trying for awhile I managed to beat the game again and Neo XYX looks great at 1080P and 60FPS!
